    <stitle>International&#174; MaxxForce&#8482; 5 Engine Service Manual - Dual Stage Turbocharger Assembly -
        Installation - Turbocharger and Exhaust Tube Torque Sequence
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc graphiccount="1">
        <title>Turbocharger and Exhaust Tube Torque Sequence</title>
        <figure id="f3900004" figsize="pg-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figN15/N15014.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="502px"/>
            <caption>Exhaust tube assembly</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">M8 x 55 bolt (3)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">M8 x 50 bolts and M8 nuts (4)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">M8 x 27 bolt (3)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">M10 x 30 high temp bolts (4)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">V-band clamp (crossover tube)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Turbine V-band clamp</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1 id="s0413">
            <para count="1">Tighten three M8 x 55 turbocharger mounting bolts to
                <hotlnk document="eges390_373.xml" xrefid="S300GTG">standard torque</hotlnk>
                <xref refid="S300GTG"/>.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tighten two M8 x 50 bolts and nuts securing the exhaust tube assembly to each exhaust
                manifold in the following order:
            </para>
            <seqlist>
                <item>
                    <para>Tighten M8 x 50 bolts and nuts to 10.3 N&#183;m (91 lbf&#183;in).</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Tighten M8 x 50 bolts and nuts to 20.6 N&#183;m (183 lbf&#183;in).</para>
                </item>
                <item>
                    <para>Tighten M8 x 50 bolts and nuts to 31 N&#183;m (23 lbf&#183;ft).</para>
                </item>
            </seqlist>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tighten three M8 x 27 bolts securing the exhaust tube assembly to the EGR cooler to standard
                torque.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tighten four M10 x 30 high temp bolts securing the exhaust tube assembly to the turbocharger
                to standard torque.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Tighten the crossover tube V-band clamp to
                <hotlnk document="eges390_144.xml" xrefid="t390000402">special torque</hotlnk>
                <xref refid="t390000402"/>.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Verify alignment marks are together, then tighten the turbine V-band clamp to special
                torque.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
